absolutely delicious. i found that the chocolate swirls were a bit too firm, even after the cake came to room temperature. it could be that i just didn't swirl them in enough, but i like the contrast of a mouthfull of chocolate next to the creamy cheesecake, so i think next time i will try adding slightly more cream so it doesn't get as hard. also, be very careful not to over bake. when you pull it out of the oven, you'll probably think that there is no way that it will firm up, but it does, even when it comes out looking too soft.

